Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.96,0:11:14.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們總是走不到能通車的路呢…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.88,0:11:19.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今晚就在這過夜如何？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.96,0:11:21.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麻幌 你還好吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.74,0:11:27.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我真是沒用…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.14,0:11:28.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才沒有這回事咧…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.44,0:11:29.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不不…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.14,0:11:31.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果麻幌你不在這…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.94,0:11:33.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是這樣的 阿優
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.00,0:11:37.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這時候有點對不起阿優 可是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.53,0:11:42.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,該怎麼說咧…\n我覺得我現在很高興…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.92,0:11:46.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我沒有總部那些人的協助 \n就會變得很無助…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.56,0:11:48.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麻幌…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.26,0:11:53.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我感到我能做到目前這樣…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.70,0:11:57.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都是因為有周圍的人在支持與鼓勵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.16,0:12:03.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是 對我來說…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.50,0:12:05.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算是麻幌一個人也已經幫了我很多忙了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.59,0:12:10.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要的只是你一直陪伴在我身邊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.94,0:12:13.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,光是那樣我就滿足了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.98,0:12:17.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還記得麻幌跟我去橫濱的約會嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.68,0:12:22.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯！那時候式條老師一直糾纏著我們真是麻煩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.71,0:12:25.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 可是那倒幫了我一個大忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.87,0:12:27.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,約會的時候我一直很不自在…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.92,0:12:29.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那讓我覺得有一點背悲傷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.36,0:12:31.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當然會覺得害羞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.30,0:12:34.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一直看著對方時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.81,0:12:37.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,二人之間的一切似乎都消失了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.52,0:12:41.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,消失得過頭突然變得害怕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.59,0:12:45.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以 我東張西望看看周圍…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.34,0:12:48.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是 當我再轉過頭看她的時候…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.40,0:12:51.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她會不在原來的地方了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.52,0:12:53.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有這種感覺…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.99,0:13:06.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,海…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.06,0:13:08.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這附近有海！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.59,0:13:13.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,海…？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.45,0:13:54.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,美裡司令曾經告訴我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.88,0:13:58.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在這世界上有更美麗的事物…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.00,0:14:00.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,更美麗的事物？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:01.39,0:14:04.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我終於知道那是什麼了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.26,0:14:09.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就是跟你喜歡的人\n一起看著的夕陽…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.07,0:14:14.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯真的呢…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.52,0:14:56.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天快要黑了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.39,0:15:03.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,呃 那個…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.76,0:15:05.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麻…幌…？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.50,0:15:07.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:12.69,0:15:13.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿優…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.56,0:15:18.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們現在處於很緊急的狀況 \n不應該做那種事…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:21.01,0:15:23.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼？\n換上戰鬥服有什麼不對的嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.33,0:15:26.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,晚上的森林是很危險的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.56,0:15:29.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到天亮之前我會一直保護你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.30,0:15:33.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,呃 是這樣嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.16,0:15:37.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.51,0:15:43.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是…你怎麼找到這裡的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.33,0:15:46.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓你吃驚了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:46.80,0:15:47.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.91,0:15:51.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別擔心 我得興趣不是偷襲你們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.35,0:15:52.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是說這個！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.06,0:15:55.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,偷看女生換衣服是沒常識的人！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.46,0:15:56.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.56,0:15:59.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起對不起 我正巧路過這
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.65,0:16:01.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,…透過追蹤你的領針
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.88,0:16:06.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我早就該發覺這點的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.77,0:16:25.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿優！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.99,0:16:28.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿優 對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.57,0:16:29.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你沒事吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.54,0:16:32.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…只是樹枝碰到臉而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.15,0:16:36.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算我可以和貝魯德拉斯戰鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.94,0:16:38.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是我不可能同時保護阿優…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.75,0:16:40.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我現在該怎麼辦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.89,0:16:45.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他沒有跟著我們過來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.40,0:16:59.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有人說過攻擊就是最好的防禦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.37,0:17:01.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麻幌？你要做什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:01.79,0:17:05.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿優 請跑得越遠越好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.62,0:17:07.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要擊倒貝魯德拉斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.42,0:17:12.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麻幌她要離開我了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.62,0:17:16.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麻幌她要離開我了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.82,0:17:20.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麻幌她…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.27,0:17:24.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 不！你不可以這樣走了！\n你說過你哪裡都不去的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.02,0:17:27.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你說過會永遠跟我在一起的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.89,0:17:33.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎樣 你都會永遠跟我在一起不是嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.95,0:17:49.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.71,0:17:52.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿優…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:52.81,0:17:55.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我會永遠跟你在一起的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:03.93,0:18:05.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道離這有多遠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.34,0:18:08.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是只要你一直沿著海岸往南走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.72,0:18:10.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,應該會碰到一個叫做坎比齊的港都
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.76,0:18:12.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們就約在那碰面吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:14.11,0:18:15.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你一定要來喔！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.22,0:18:18.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.44,0:18:19.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.17,0:18:35.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果這是個陷阱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.54,0:18:38.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕美里優早就死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.49,0:18:40.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你從來沒想過這點嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:41.58,0:18:45.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你從來就沒有打算要等到我的機能停止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.73,0:18:48.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你一開始的目的就是要跟我戰鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.73,0:18:52.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果不是這樣\n你剛剛就不會跟蹤我們到這了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.27,0:18:54.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.48,0:18:56.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然你和我是不同的造型
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.04,0:18:59.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是我們都是只為了戰鬥而存在的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:00.66,0:19:01.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以 我想戰鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:44.03,0:19:45.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是有趣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.74,0:19:48.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這武器似乎能無限制地變強
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.14,0:20:03.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像地球也變成兩半了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:06.49,0:20:09.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不知道這武器的真正使用方法！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:31.06,0:20:32.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麻幌！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.89,0:20:36.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麻幌！麻…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:50.98,0:23:00.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(276,250)\fs24\fad(1200,4000)}往最終話…
